sequenceDiagram
    actor U as User
    participant B as Browser
    participant BE as Backend
    participant NA as Naver Auth
    participant NR as Naver Resource

    U->>B: 네이버 로그인 클릭
    B->>BE: GET /oauth2/authorization/naver

    Note over BE: state 생성
    Note over BE: OAuth2AuthorizationRequest 생성
    Note over BE: 기본값이면 HttpSession에 저장

    BE-->>B: 302 Redirect to Naver authorize URL + Set-Cookie(JSESSIONID)
    Note over B: JSESSIONID 저장
    Note over B: authorize URL 안에는 state 포함

    B->>NA: GET /oauth2.0/authorize?...&state=abc123
    NA-->>B: 302 Redirect to /login/oauth2/code/naver?code=AUTH_CODE&state=abc123

    B->>BE: GET /login/oauth2/code/naver?code=AUTH_CODE&state=abc123 + Cookie:JSESSIONID
    Note over BE: JSESSIONID로 저장된 AuthorizationRequest 조회
    Note over BE: 저장된 state 와 돌아온 state 비교

    alt state 일치
        BE->>NA: POST /oauth2.0/token (AUTH_CODE)
        NA-->>BE: access_token
        BE->>NR: GET /v1/nid/me (Bearer access_token)
        NR-->>BE: user info
        BE-->>B: 302 Redirect to frontend callback?code=EXCHANGE_CODE
    else state 불일치 또는 없음
        BE-->>B: OAuth2FailureHandler 로 실패 리다이렉트
    end
